defaultVerges host delightful (and sometimes rare) flora and provide migration routes for some animals, amphibians and reptiles. The NPA has designated a number of Road Verge Reserves. Although technically part of the right of way, verges are vulnerable to damage when vehicles need to pass each other and PDNPA are concerned about this damage to the environment.
